NAME
    Task::POE::All - Installs all the modules in the POE::* namespace (
    latest version )

DESCRIPTION
    This module will use CPANPLUS to retrieve all the modules under the
    POE::* namespace and install them.

SEE ALSO
    POE

SUPPORT
    You can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

            perldoc Task::POE::All

