  Bugs
    Please report any bugs or feature requests to "bug-task-poe-all at
    rt.cpan.org", or through the web interface at
    <http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/ReportBug.html?Queue=Task-POE-All>. I will be
    notified, and then you'll automatically be notified of progress on your
    bug as I make changes.

